Product name: Sterling Silver Ranger Buckle Set
Description:
Sterling silver ranger buckle set.
The Texas Rangers made this style popular.  
You need the right belt style to use this buckle.
Sometimes the belt is narrow in front and sometimes the belt has
a narrow piece sewn to the front of a wider belt.
The buckle is 2 1/8" long x 1 5/8" wide.  The belt front must be 5/8" or
less.  There are 2 keepers and a tip. The tip has a prong to press into
the leather to keep it secure. 
Stamped sterling.
Good vintage condition with natural patina.
Shipped by US first class mail and insured.
